{
  "texts": [
    "Using only four entity types leads to a severely skewed distributions of entity types due to the limited data.",
    "The appropriate use of datasets is important.",
    "we exclude datasets that focus on evaluating tabular time series data using a standard language model.",
    "there is reasons to believe and show interest in transformers and decoders as symbolic reasoners over time series numerical data, but language models are not trained for time series forecasting.",
    "As others have noted (Wu et al., 2024) this type of data and task tend to be ineffective and not useful for understanding the capability of a language model to generate a forecast."
  ]
}